wiki.content: On the second track of ME here’s JISOO with the release of “All Eyes On Me” an electronic upbeat dance-pop anthem that showcases her enchanting visuals. Taking a look in the lyrics, JISOO lores others focus onto her in order for her to take a deep sight into their heart. The aforementioned instrumental compliments the confidence and dreamy feel of JISOO’s vocals. The aesthetic of the song was described by JISOO on an interview with Naver: The affection for ‘All Eyes On Me’ is so special that it was prepared as a candidate for the title song. Feeling cheerful yet deadly? “The affection for ‘All Eyes On Me’ is so special that it was prepared as a candidate for the title song. Feeling cheerful yet deadly? I think a lot of people will like it as much as I do.“ — JISOO via Naver Read more on Last.fm.
